nhc_headline: ...HIGH SURF EXPECTED AND TROPICAL STORM CONDITIONS POSSIBLE FOR BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR OVER THE NEXT DAY AS PRISCILLA MOVES PARALLEL TO THE PACIFIC COAST OF MEXICO...
summary: ...HIGH SURF EXPECTED AND TROPICAL STORM CONDITIONS POSSIBLE FOR BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR OVER THE NEXT DAY AS PRISCILLA MOVES PARALLEL TO THE PACIFIC COAST OF MEXICO... As of 11:00 PM MST Tue Oct 07 the center of Priscilla was located near 20.9, -111.8 with movement NW at 9 mph. The minimum central pressure was 962 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 105 mph.
